The paper discusses the use of natural language expressions annotated with images, which falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the creation of datasets and tasks for computational semantics, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
